### Get refunds
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/refunds?page=1&limit=20&status=PENDING&type=CANCEL_REFUND
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN}}

### Get refund detail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/refunds/{{REFUND_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN}}

### Retry refund
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/refunds/{{REFUND_ID}}/retry
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}